<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹lyk rfʿt ṣlạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - (ạ̹lyk rfʿt ṣlạty wqlby yhtf bạldʿạʾ
 ạ̉mạmk ạ̉skb dẖạty ʿynạy trnw ạ̹ly̱ ạlsmạʾ)2
 ạ̉tyt bạ̹ḥtyạjy wkẖwfy ạlsẖdyd bḍyqy wạnzʿạdy fạ̹nny wḥyd
 yạ sạmʿ ạlṣlạẗ ạstjbt tḍrʿạty ( yạ mạlkạaⁿ ḥyạty bḥbk ạlfryd )2
 1- (qd ḍạq zmạny hạ ạ̹ny ạ̉ʿạny krbạaⁿ fy drwby fqrạaⁿ fy jywby
 ktẖrt ạ̉wjạʿy wạ̉nhạr dfạʿy lys ly ṣdyqạaⁿ ạlywm swạk)2
 2- (ḥbk yạ ạ̹lhy gẖyr mtnạhy yḥyạ fy ḍlwʿy fy sẖkẖṣ yswʿ
 rwḥk yḥyyny ysẖfʿ lạ̉nyny wqt ạlạ̉zmạt lys ly swạk)2</lyrics>
<author>ạ̉ymn kfrwny, ạ̉ymn kfrwny</author>
<hymn_number>2058</hymn_number>
</song>